The picture (same angle, same people, but cropped slightly) was published in &quot;Randwick, a Social History&quot; (Randwick Council 1985) and captioned:

&quot;The Bondi Aquarium at Tamarama opened in 1887.  It is pictured here in about 1891, after rebuilding following a fire&quot;
It is attributed to Australian Consolidated Press Ltd.
